description: I woke up today a little bit late. But I noticed that I already had 3 missed calls that morning. As nobody used the answering machine I called that person back. The guy on the other end had a sexy voice. But he seemed to be nervous and shy. I promised to visit him in the evening. I was a bit surprised when I came there as the house was modern and clean. Usually my clients live under different conditions. I took the elevator and I was surprised again - a girl welcomed me upstairs. Now I was nervous. Obviously I forgot to tell the guy that I have to speak with him alone - this is usually an important information. Anyway. When I came in I saw a real cutie. But desperate. I decided to try to ignore the girl.
title: Debt Dandy 06
